<view class="page">
  <view wx:if="{{errorText}}" class="state-card warning">{{errorText}}</view>

  <view class="card status-card">
    <view class="label">今日服药状态</view>
    <view class="status">{{completedToday ? '已完成' : '待记录'}}</view>
    <view class="operation-time">系统操作时间：{{lastOperationTime}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="label">明日剂量记录模式</view>
    <picker mode="selector" range="{{doseOptions}}" range-key="label" value="{{doseModeIndex}}" bindchange="onDoseModeChange">
      <view class="picker-value">{{doseOptions[doseModeIndex].label}}</view>
    </picker>
    <input wx:if="{{doseOptions[doseModeIndex].value === 'manual'}}" class="input" type="digit" value="{{manualDoseInput}}" bindinput="onManualDoseInput" placeholder="输入医生已确认剂量 mg" />
    <view class="note">仅选择“按既定计划”或记录已确认剂量，不生成任何剂量建议。</view>
  </view>

  <button class="primary-button" loading="{{submitting}}" disabled="{{submitting}}" bindtap="onCompleteMedication">完成今日服药</button>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="label">最近记录</view>
    <view class="value">{{tomorrowDoseText}}</view>
    <view class="note">仅记录用户选择和系统操作时间，不包含补服或剂量建议。</view>
  </view>
</view>
